{"tid":191574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一次食得最豪的經驗","createTime":"2017-04-08T04:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T07:47:21.000Z","uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1952649cd91bd12326183f99ac23c1a460299f3","tid":191574,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有次多左錢，想食豪點。個時我慢慢抬起頭，望住收銀員姐姐，緩慢，但強而有力地說，要一碗大牛肉飯，同埋一杯水。個下我覺得自己大膽到好似講緊「我要十個」一樣。之後我放低左兩張紫色的十元紙幣。再逐個逐個一元硬幣放係枱面。最後滿足地轉身離開，等待夢寐已久的牛肉飯，大碗的。"},{"pid":"b0e1c814cfd21740927c8eeb10362b86eec94d61","tid":191574,"uid":37152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"9ff62b0d478f1bb819271db9134f214b880450b4","tid":191574,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"渣ga, me譚過橋"},{"pid":"72e9c1eff86cc866bf51ade237fa78e1b088ffe2","tid":191574,"uid":78322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"2675f0c35aac42f489e0aba9ca3df241eabbd006","tid":191574,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"嘻"},{"pid":"33fd3ff2382cb7bc283ddfc1beb0723e3566fcb7","tid":191574,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"生日同事請我去Ruth's Chris Steak House食...over 1000 per 人<br />\n冇下次~~~~"},{"pid":"2258088343c746eb360a84da31fa69b26b400f01","tid":191574,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"真正既一餐飯"},{"pid":"1c5888df99bbac14f08ec024c06ca489d26b4891","tid":191574,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日同事請我去Ruth's Chris Steak House食...over 1000 per 人<br />\n冇下次~~~~</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次同女朋友去Ruth's Chris 2條友食咗3000幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab47db5d4270d20d5d38d1f5467e857207a4040",